org.apache.edgent.providers.direct

Class DirectTopology

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.edgent.topology.spi.AbstractTopology<X>
      • org.apache.edgent.topology.spi.graph.GraphTopology<org.apache.edgent.providers.direct.DirectTester>
        • org.apache.edgent.providers.direct.DirectTopology
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Topology, TopologyElement

    public class DirectTopology
extends GraphTopology<org.apache.edgent.providers.direct.DirectTester>
    DirectTopology is a GraphTopology that is executed in threads in the current virtual machine.

    The topology is backed by a DirectGraph and its execution is controlled and monitored by a EtiaoJob.
